INSTALLATION

To install Test::Critic with C<make> give the following commands to
your favorite shell:

  tar -zxf Test-Critic-0.01.tar.gz
  cd Test-Critic-0.01
  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make test
  make install 

Or if you prefer C<Module::Build>, try this:

  tar -zxf Test-Critic-0.01.tar.gz
  cd Test-Critic-0.01
  perl Build.pl
  ./Build
  ./Build test
  ./Build install 